1
00:01:37,079 --> 00:01:37,760
Miss,

2
00:01:38,079 --> 00:01:39,799
is Mr. Chen Yanyun proposing to you?

3
00:01:41,519 --> 00:01:42,599
He just said

4
00:01:42,599 --> 00:01:43,920
he'd been to Tongzhou.

5
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:46,680
So he talked about it to your grandmother.

6
00:01:47,439 --> 00:01:48,680
Did she say yes?

7
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:53,519
Wonderful!

8
00:01:55,799 --> 00:01:56,799
I can't believe

9
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,000
you're really getting married.

10
00:02:01,799 --> 00:02:03,400
Feels like a dream.

11
00:02:04,359 --> 00:02:05,200
Same here.

12
00:02:07,879 --> 00:02:09,120
Something feels off.

13
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,439
I can't put my finger on it.

14
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:15,240
I have something tricky

15
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,719
to deal with right now.

16
00:02:19,319 --> 00:02:20,520
Got it.

17
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:21,560
Thank you.

18
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:28,800
Miss.

19
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:33,400
So?

20
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:34,719
The gatekeeper said
Mr. Ye Xian is on duty

21
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:36,599
at the palace these days.

22
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,199
Won't be out for a few more days.

23
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,840
Of all times.

24
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:43,599
But Guard Li came back once

25
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,719
to pick up a change of clothes for Mr. Ye.

26
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:46,879
Miss,

27
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,719
why don't you write a letter?

28
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,919
I'll find a way to give it to Guard Li

29
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:53,759
and have him pass it to Mr. Ye.

30
00:02:55,039 --> 00:02:55,680
No.

31
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,159
I have to

32
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,840
tell him this in person.

33
00:02:59,319 --> 00:03:01,000
Otherwise, I'd be disrespecting him.

34
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:05,080
This is all my fault.

35
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,000
I should've told him sooner.

36
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,199
Lie down.

37
00:03:12,439 --> 00:03:12,800
There.

38
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:17,639
Ye Xian,

39
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,680
you've got the touch.

40
00:03:19,439 --> 00:03:20,400
In just a few days,

41
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:21,360
Frost's condition
has gotten better day by day.

42
00:03:22,639 --> 00:03:23,360
It eats, sleeps,
runs and plays normally now.

43
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,360
I think

44
00:03:25,639 --> 00:03:26,520
he just takes to you.

45
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:28,719
Your Majesty, you flatter me.

46
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:29,919
If you ask me,

47
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,560
Frost doesn't take to me.

48
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:32,800
He takes to

49
00:03:32,879 --> 00:03:33,840
the jerky

50
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:35,000
I bring from outside.

51
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,000
Come on, Frost.

52
00:03:42,439 --> 00:03:44,280
Looks like he's tired of palace food

53
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,800
and is craving something new.

54
00:03:46,159 --> 00:03:47,319
Even a dog feels that way,

55
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:48,240
let alone a person.

56
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,080
Speaking of which,

57
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,319
something strange
just came to mind.

58
00:03:53,719 --> 00:03:55,080
The other day, I had a scratchy throat

59
00:03:55,639 --> 00:03:56,520
and wanted some pear soup.

60
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:57,919
I ordered it,

61
00:03:58,319 --> 00:03:59,319
but ended up waiting an hour
before I got it.

62
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:01,599
Then yesterday,

63
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,240
when Mr. Fu came to tutor me,

64
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,599
he wanted pear soup too.

65
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:05,919
Within moments,

66
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,159
it was brought up.

67
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,400
And it was just to his liking.

68
00:04:09,159 --> 00:04:10,599
I found it odd,

69
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,719
so I sent someone to ask.

70
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:14,599
And guess what?

71
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:17,000
Turns out, the kitchen at Huangji Hall

72
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,199
always keeps pear soup

73
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,800
and sweet bean paste warming

74
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,000
on the stove for Mr. Fu.

75
00:04:23,519 --> 00:04:25,000
Now that's strange.

76
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:29,800
Come to think of it,

77
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,439
I've come across

78
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:33,120
something odd myself lately.

79
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:34,920
Tell me about it.

80
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,920
You know the Criminal Investigation Bureau

81
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,959
has a record office?

82
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,759
The late Emperor told me about it.

83
00:04:42,199 --> 00:04:43,360
The Criminal Investigation Bureau

84
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,680
kept all the records

85
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:45,519
on official oversight there.

86
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:46,680
That's right.

87
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,319
There are records on all officials.

88
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:49,959
Except for

89
00:04:49,959 --> 00:04:51,279
one person.

90
00:04:52,959 --> 00:04:53,959
Isn't that strange,

91
00:04:54,279 --> 00:04:55,199
Your Majesty?

92
00:04:58,519 --> 00:04:59,399
Strange.

93
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:02,000
Yours is even stranger.

94
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:05,279
Yanyun, rest assured.

95
00:05:05,439 --> 00:05:07,240
Leave this to me and my wife.

96
00:05:08,199 --> 00:05:08,680
Alright.

97
00:05:09,199 --> 00:05:10,079
Many thanks

98
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,560
to you and your wife.

99
00:05:13,399 --> 00:05:14,879
I'm jealous of you, Yanyun.

100
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,319
Carefree and easy.

101
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:18,279
And about to welcome great joy.

102
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:19,199
Unlike me.

103
00:05:19,319 --> 00:05:20,319
First, Mr. Fan Chuan

104
00:05:20,319 --> 00:05:21,680
left the Grand Secretariat.

105
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,680
Now you're gone too.

106
00:05:22,959 --> 00:05:24,319
I'm spinning like a top.

107
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,839
You have no idea,

108
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:27,319
the memorials are piled up that high.

109
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,160
I even told the Chief Councilor today

110
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,399
to bring you back as soon as possible.

111
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:31,839
Oh, you.

112
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,959
Seeing

113
00:05:36,319 --> 00:05:37,519
all the court officials work so hard,

114
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,079
devoted to their duties

115
00:05:39,519 --> 00:05:40,680
and the nation,

116
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,319
exhausting themselves,

117
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:43,879
actually gives me comfort.

118
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:46,319
To show my consideration for you all,

119
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:49,519
I hereby abolish the position of Inspector.

120
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:52,639
May we work as one from now on,

121
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,360
govern together,

122
00:05:54,839 --> 00:05:56,759
and bring peace to the people.

123
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:06,399
Your Majesty, you are wise.

124
00:06:06,399 --> 00:06:11,120
Long live Your Majesty.

125
00:06:20,439 --> 00:06:20,959
Miss.

126
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,399
So?
Did you see him?

127
00:06:27,079 --> 00:06:28,399
The Criminal Investigation Bureau caught fire.

128
00:06:28,399 --> 00:06:29,560
Many places burned down.

129
00:06:29,759 --> 00:06:31,040
Mr. Ye is too busy to get away.

130
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:39,279
I heard from Master

131
00:06:39,279 --> 00:06:40,759
that the Chief Councilor's face

132
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,079
was dark when court ended.

133
00:06:43,959 --> 00:06:44,800
Looks like
even he didn't know

134
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:47,439
His Majesty was going to abolish

135
00:06:47,959 --> 00:06:49,560
the Inspector position.

136
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:53,920
Old Madam.

137
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:55,279
Second Madam.

138
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,680
Mrs. Yao is here.

139
00:06:58,959 --> 00:07:00,279
She was meant to get here at noon.

140
00:07:00,639 --> 00:07:01,680
She's early.

141
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:03,879
She must be

142
00:07:04,199 --> 00:07:05,360
eager about

143
00:07:05,639 --> 00:07:07,000
Lian and Yao Wenxiu's wedding.

144
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,680
You should go.

145
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:14,800
Mother, come with me.

146
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,120
Such an important matter

147
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:17,680
is for you to decide.

148
00:07:18,959 --> 00:07:19,759
True.

149
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,199
Xiuju. Xiuju.

150
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,959
Go listen over there.

151
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,000
Come back and tell me
if anything happens.

152
00:07:40,439 --> 00:07:41,399
Yes, miss.

153
00:07:57,319 --> 00:07:58,839
What do I do?

154
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,519
Mrs. Yao is probably here

155
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,680
to set

156
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,959
a wedding date

157
00:08:02,959 --> 00:08:03,879
for Wenxiu and me.

158
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:16,920
We're late.

159
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:17,879
Mrs. Yao.

160
00:08:18,079 --> 00:08:18,959
- Sorry to keep you waiting.
- Old Madam.

161
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,439
Not at all.

162
00:08:20,639 --> 00:08:22,000
I came early.

163
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:23,839
Take a seat.

164
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,040
I'm here

165
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:30,519
about Wenxiu

166
00:08:30,519 --> 00:08:32,240
and Lian's marriage.

167
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:36,240
Yes.

168
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,799
After the New Year, Wenxiu turns 18

169
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:40,399
and Lian turns 17.

170
00:08:40,639 --> 00:08:41,879
It's time to set a date.

171
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:45,240
Have you had a date picked yet?

172
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,440
Why?

173
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,240
Is something wrong?

174
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:02,120
Do you think the end of the year is better,

175
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:04,200
or early spring next year?

176
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:08,080
I'm hoping for early spring.

177
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:10,519
It'll be warmer.

178
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,840
And the clothes look nicer.

179
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,879
I hear brides have

180
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:21,320
a really hard time.

181
00:09:21,799 --> 00:09:23,200
Lucky you two.

182
00:09:23,399 --> 00:09:24,639
You don't have to worry about that.

183
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,120
After all,

184
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,799
your reputation is bad.

185
00:09:28,159 --> 00:09:28,879
And your mother

186
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,200
committed a crime.

187
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:31,720
Neither of you is easy to marry off.

188
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:37,080
Are you silly?

189
00:09:39,279 --> 00:09:40,120
What did you say?

190
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:41,840
Are you really that clueless

191
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,000
or just pretending?

192
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:45,480
Mr. Yao is the Vice Minister of Justice,

193
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,559
but he has four sons.

194
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,960
Yao Wenxiu

195
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,120
is the youngest.

196
00:09:50,799 --> 00:09:51,799
By the time the family assets
get split up to him,

197
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,480
there'll be barely anything left.

198
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:56,600
And he's got no talent of his own.

199
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:58,559
He's just a provincial scholar now.

200
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:00,159
If he never gets an official post

201
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,639
and the family gives him nothing,

202
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,720
after you marry him,

203
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:03,919
the two of you

204
00:10:04,159 --> 00:10:05,840
will be living off your dowry.

205
00:10:06,759 --> 00:10:07,600
If I were you,

206
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,000
I'd be worried sick.

207
00:10:09,279 --> 00:10:10,919
How can you be so happy about it?

208
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:12,799
Gu Jinzhao, you...

209
00:10:15,919 --> 00:10:17,440
Don't act so high and mighty

210
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,679
just because you have some money.

211
00:10:19,399 --> 00:10:20,200
Let me tell you,

212
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,080
after I marry Wenxiu,

213
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,159
I'll make sure

214
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:24,320
all your business ventures fail!

215
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,679
Are you laughing at me?

216
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,320
No.

217
00:10:31,919 --> 00:10:33,399
How would I dare laugh at you?

218
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:35,679
I... I really envy you.

219
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:43,480
You're acting strange.

220
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,799
Are you plotting something?

221
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:47,679
Miss!

222
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:50,759
Miss.

223
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:54,919
So?

224
00:10:55,159 --> 00:10:57,000
End of the year or early spring?

225
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,000
Neither.

226
00:10:58,559 --> 00:10:59,600
Mrs. Yao said...

227
00:11:00,639 --> 00:11:01,720
She wants to call off the engagement.

228
00:11:04,879 --> 00:11:06,000
Call off the engagement?

229
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:09,559
Why?

230
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:10,600
I don't know.

231
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:13,159
You don't know? You stupid girl!

232
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,679
The second I heard them say that,

233
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,840
I ran straight back.

234
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,759
Didn't hear anything after that.

235
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,000
No.

236
00:11:20,759 --> 00:11:22,440
I have to go find out why.

237
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,600
Miss, you can't go.

238
00:11:25,399 --> 00:11:26,480
Why can't I?

239
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,679
They want to call off the engagement.

240
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,600
You'd just
embarrass yourself.

241
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:44,840
Was it you?

242
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,600
I know

243
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,200
it was you.

244
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,120
You're the only one

245
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,440
who could pull something like this.

246
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,960
You hold a grudge against me.

247
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,480
So you schemed to make the Yaos

248
00:11:55,799 --> 00:11:57,240
call off the engagement.

249
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,759
Was it you?

250
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:00,440
If they call off the engagement,

251
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,200
it will bring shame

252
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,240
on the entire Gu family.

253
00:12:02,759 --> 00:12:04,120
What good does that do me?

254
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:05,840
Unbelievable.

255
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,200
Lan, let's go.

256
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,360
Don't you leave!

257
00:12:10,279 --> 00:12:11,840
Even if it wasn't you, it's your fault.

258
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,559
Because of you guys,

259
00:12:13,919 --> 00:12:15,360
my father went to prison

260
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:16,559
and his reputation was ruined.

261
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,679
So the Yaos called the engagement off!

262
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,159
Like I said,

263
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,440
ever since you moved back,

264
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:24,960
our family has had nothing but bad luck

265
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:26,279
after bad luck!

266
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:27,720
You...

267
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,799
You bunch of jinxes!

268
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,000
Bad omens!

269
00:12:32,279 --> 00:12:33,559
If the Yaos call off the engagement

270
00:12:33,559 --> 00:12:34,600
for that reason,

271
00:12:34,919 --> 00:12:36,080
then it's actually a good thing

272
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:36,600
for you not to

273
00:12:36,879 --> 00:12:38,519
marry into such a snobbish family.

274
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,080
You're just wishing this

275
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:42,080
would happen, right?

276
00:12:42,679 --> 00:12:44,320
You can't get married yourself,

277
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:46,240
so you're jealous that I found a good match.

278
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,360
Maybe Yao Wenxiu

279
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,240
doesn't like you

280
00:12:51,559 --> 00:12:53,080
and wanted to call it off all along.

281
00:12:53,919 --> 00:12:55,399
You're lying!

282
00:12:55,399 --> 00:12:56,879
I'll tear your mouth apart!

283
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:58,759
Jinzhao!

284
00:13:01,759 --> 00:13:03,240
Who dares to bully Jinzhao?

285
00:13:05,759 --> 00:13:06,399
Anyway,

286
00:13:06,399 --> 00:13:08,320
we're sorry.

287
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:10,200
We won't

288
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:11,039
take back
the betrothal gifts.

289
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:14,080
Consider them an apology.

290
00:13:15,039 --> 00:13:16,320
But no matter what,

291
00:13:16,679 --> 00:13:17,919
this engagement

292
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,600
must be called off.

293
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,759
Old Madam, Second Madam.

294
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,039
Trouble!

295
00:13:26,519 --> 00:13:27,879
Miss Lian, Miss Jinzhao,

296
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:28,720
Miss Lan,

297
00:13:28,799 --> 00:13:30,279
and Jinrong are fighting.

298
00:13:30,519 --> 00:13:32,159
Miss Lian hit Miss Lan.

299
00:13:32,159 --> 00:13:33,000
Jinrong...

300
00:13:33,639 --> 00:13:34,320
Useless!

301
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:35,559
Get out!

302
00:13:36,039 --> 00:13:37,240
No manners!

303
00:13:40,679 --> 00:13:42,519
Lian even hit people?

304
00:13:42,759 --> 00:13:44,039
Such a temper.

305
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:45,720
Who can handle that?

306
00:13:47,559 --> 00:13:48,519
Well,

307
00:13:49,559 --> 00:13:51,360
I've said what I came to say.

308
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:54,360
Please make a decision soon.

309
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:56,159
Don't drag this out.

310
00:13:58,519 --> 00:13:59,759
Old Madam, Second Madam.

311
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,000
Quick.

312
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:01,879
Outrageous!

313
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:03,720
This is outrageous!

314
00:14:06,559 --> 00:14:08,320
Old Madam, Second Madam, calm down.

315
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:11,080
I don't mean to break the rules.

316
00:14:11,279 --> 00:14:12,120
But

317
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:13,519
Mrs. He

318
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:15,080
is already at the gate.

319
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:17,240
Mrs. He?

320
00:14:17,639 --> 00:14:18,600
Which Mrs. He?

321
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:19,759
The wife

322
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:21,120
of Grand Secretary

323
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:23,000
He Wenxin.

324
00:14:23,159 --> 00:14:24,639
Mrs. He is here?

325
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,000
What,

326
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,759
you have ties

327
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:31,120
with Mrs. He?

328
00:14:31,279 --> 00:14:32,159
Hurry up.

329
00:14:32,159 --> 00:14:33,240
Open the main gate to receive her.

330
00:14:33,399 --> 00:14:34,000
Yes.

331
00:14:37,399 --> 00:14:38,600
We're terribly busy today.

332
00:14:38,759 --> 00:14:39,600
We won't keep you.

333
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:40,919
Cuilyu, see her out.

334
00:14:40,919 --> 00:14:41,559
Indeed.

335
00:14:41,559 --> 00:14:43,039
Receiving Mrs. He takes priority.

336
00:14:43,039 --> 00:14:44,240
I'll go back and discuss

337
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:45,720
the engagement cancellation further.

338
00:14:46,399 --> 00:14:48,240
Let's not rush into anything.

339
00:15:04,919 --> 00:15:06,000
My... my stomach

340
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,120
feels a bit off.

341
00:15:07,919 --> 00:15:09,360
Take me to freshen up.

342
00:15:10,279 --> 00:15:10,879
Yes.

343
00:15:11,159 --> 00:15:12,279
Please follow me.

344
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:24,679
Welcome, Mrs. He!

345
00:15:25,559 --> 00:15:26,200
This way.

346
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,000
Please.

347
00:15:33,799 --> 00:15:35,759
I should've sent a calling card.

348
00:15:35,919 --> 00:15:36,919
But since our families

349
00:15:36,919 --> 00:15:38,279
don't associate much,

350
00:15:38,519 --> 00:15:39,879
I worried that sending a card

351
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:41,600
might only disturb your household.

352
00:15:42,279 --> 00:15:43,240
I

353
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:44,519
am always in a hurry.

354
00:15:44,919 --> 00:15:46,360
And the person who asked me to do this

355
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:47,759
is even more impatient.

356
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:48,639
So

357
00:15:48,759 --> 00:15:50,240
I decided to just come here.

358
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:52,159
Please don't take offense.

359
00:15:53,639 --> 00:15:54,679
Not at all.

360
00:15:55,279 --> 00:15:56,360
Your visit

361
00:15:56,559 --> 00:15:58,080
is an honor to us.

362
00:15:59,000 --> 00:15:59,919
May I ask

363
00:16:01,039 --> 00:16:03,360
what brings you here?

364
00:16:04,039 --> 00:16:05,320
Old Madam, please sit.

365
00:16:08,759 --> 00:16:10,039
It's good news, of course.

366
00:16:10,559 --> 00:16:11,440
Someone sent me to ask

367
00:16:11,559 --> 00:16:13,559
Miss Jinzhao for her hand in marriage.

368
00:16:14,559 --> 00:16:15,480
Jinzhao?

369
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,679
Who

370
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:21,399
has the influence

371
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:24,080
to ask you to be the matchmaker?

372
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:26,080
Who else could it be?

373
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:27,879
None other than the most promising

374
00:16:27,879 --> 00:16:29,399
young official in Great Yan,

375
00:16:29,639 --> 00:16:31,639
Mr. Chen Yanyun.

376
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:36,879
What?

377
00:16:37,240 --> 00:16:38,720
Mr. Chen is proposing to Jinzhao?

378
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:39,840
Yes.
Mr. Chen

379
00:16:40,879 --> 00:16:42,159
invited Grand Secretary He's wife

380
00:16:42,519 --> 00:16:43,440
to be the matchmaker.

381
00:16:43,679 --> 00:16:45,039
Old Madam and Second Madam

382
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:46,000
are hosting her right now.

383
00:16:46,159 --> 00:16:46,759
Miss Jinzhao,
Old Madam sent me

384
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:49,000
to let you know,

385
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:51,000
so you're aware.

386
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:52,480
Congratulations, Miss Jinzhao.

387
00:16:52,639 --> 00:16:53,840
Best wishes.

388
00:17:03,279 --> 00:17:04,119
What did you say?

389
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:07,480
Chen Yanyun proposed to Gu Jinzhao

390
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:09,079
and got Grand Secretary He's wife

391
00:17:09,079 --> 00:17:10,119
to be the matchmaker?

392
00:17:18,319 --> 00:17:19,319
Miss, miss.

393
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,160
Don't be mad.

394
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:22,599
It'll ruin your health.

395
00:17:22,599 --> 00:17:23,279
Calm down.

396
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:26,559
What did you say?

397
00:17:28,839 --> 00:17:31,000
Chen Yanyun wants to marry Miss Jinzhao?

398
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:32,920
Gu Jinzhao?

399
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:34,119
You heard correctly?

400
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:35,440
I heard it loud and clear.

401
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:36,680
No mistake.

402
00:17:38,079 --> 00:17:38,880
Oh no.

403
00:17:39,559 --> 00:17:40,319
This is bad.

404
00:17:40,599 --> 00:17:41,039
How...

405
00:17:41,359 --> 00:17:42,920
How could this happen?

406
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:46,880
We made a mistake today.

407
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,799
It seems

408
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:50,599
we can't afford to offend the Gu family.

409
00:17:51,319 --> 00:17:52,000
Madam,

410
00:17:52,279 --> 00:17:53,119
isn't Mr. Chen

411
00:17:53,119 --> 00:17:54,640
already living in retirement at home?

412
00:17:54,799 --> 00:17:55,480
Mr. Yao

413
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:56,519
is the Vice Minister of Justice.

414
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:57,559
Why should we fear him?

415
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:58,640
What do you know?

416
00:17:59,119 --> 00:18:01,079
Chen Yanyun isn't really retiring.

417
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:02,400
He's just lying low at home
to avoid the heat.

418
00:18:03,680 --> 00:18:04,799
Once it blows over,

419
00:18:04,799 --> 00:18:05,920
he'll be back.

420
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,839
He's the Chief Councilor's

421
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,759
true favorite.

422
00:18:12,319 --> 00:18:14,200
My husband can't compare with him.

423
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:18,519
Mrs. He, please take care.

424
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:30,279
I really didn't see this coming.

425
00:18:31,119 --> 00:18:32,359
But Chen Yanyun

426
00:18:33,119 --> 00:18:34,359
did come to propose.

427
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:37,000
I still
feel like

428
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:39,319
this isn't real.

429
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:41,039
Well,

430
00:18:41,599 --> 00:18:43,079
Jinzhao's birth

431
00:18:43,079 --> 00:18:44,519
and her temperament

432
00:18:44,839 --> 00:18:47,039
are unworthy of such a noble household.

433
00:18:48,759 --> 00:18:50,039
Things have come to this.

434
00:18:50,359 --> 00:18:51,599
We have to swallow it.

435
00:18:52,559 --> 00:18:55,079
Old Madam. Second Madam.

436
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:57,480
You're still here.

437
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:03,119
Mrs. Yao, how did you...

438
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:07,079
My stomach was upset earlier

439
00:19:07,559 --> 00:19:08,599
and I felt dizzy,

440
00:19:08,759 --> 00:19:10,480
so I rested here for a while.

441
00:19:10,559 --> 00:19:12,119
Knowing you were entertaining guests,

442
00:19:12,119 --> 00:19:14,160
I didn't have the servants announce me.

443
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:16,920
Mrs. He has left?

444
00:19:18,680 --> 00:19:19,440
Yes.

445
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:21,240
Since she's gone,

446
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:23,359
let's talk about our matter.

447
00:19:27,359 --> 00:19:28,799
I just thought about it.

448
00:19:29,079 --> 00:19:30,319
Calling off the engagement

449
00:19:30,519 --> 00:19:32,039
was too hasty.

450
00:19:32,440 --> 00:19:33,160
We've known each other

451
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:34,519
for so many years.

452
00:19:34,839 --> 00:19:36,200
And Wenxiu and Lian

453
00:19:36,279 --> 00:19:37,720
grew up together.

454
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:40,039
Calling it off rashly would be

455
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:42,440
breaking up a pair of lovebirds.

456
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:45,240
Mrs. Yao,

457
00:19:45,599 --> 00:19:46,920
what are you talking about?

458
00:19:47,240 --> 00:19:49,920
Lian's a proper lady from a good family,

459
00:19:50,279 --> 00:19:52,599
not some random girl.

460
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:54,759
Yes, yes.

461
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:56,279
I misspoke.

462
00:19:56,640 --> 00:19:58,480
But the engagement...

463
00:19:59,079 --> 00:20:00,599
Old Madam, what do you think...

464
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:05,359
Since

465
00:20:05,359 --> 00:20:06,640
we've come this far,

466
00:20:07,359 --> 00:20:08,640
I won't beat around the bush.

467
00:20:10,880 --> 00:20:12,519
Wenxiu and Lian's engagement

468
00:20:12,680 --> 00:20:14,160
has dragged on too long.

469
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:16,880
If you're sincere,

470
00:20:17,319 --> 00:20:18,880
then show it.

471
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:22,039
Thank you.

472
00:20:22,039 --> 00:20:23,799
I'll go back and make the preparations.

473
00:20:30,599 --> 00:20:31,279
Mother,

474
00:20:31,519 --> 00:20:33,000
the Yao family is disgusting.

475
00:20:33,119 --> 00:20:34,200
You still want Lian

476
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,640
to marry Yao Wenxiu?

477
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:36,680
What else?

478
00:20:38,519 --> 00:20:39,880
The Yao family may not be prominent,

479
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:42,079
but they're still a third-rank house.

480
00:21:00,039 --> 00:21:00,799
Miss,

481
00:21:01,079 --> 00:21:02,720
a chill follows every autumn rain.

482
00:21:03,359 --> 00:21:04,359
Don't catch a cold.

483
00:21:11,720 --> 00:21:13,000
Miss, what's wrong?

484
00:21:13,839 --> 00:21:15,039
Mr. Chen proposed.

485
00:21:15,039 --> 00:21:16,119
It's great news.

486
00:21:16,359 --> 00:21:18,000
Why are you sighing?

487
00:21:20,440 --> 00:21:21,400
I don't know.

488
00:21:21,799 --> 00:21:22,640
I knew

489
00:21:22,640 --> 00:21:24,160
he would come to propose.

490
00:21:25,079 --> 00:21:26,400
But now that it's happening,

491
00:21:27,079 --> 00:21:28,440
it doesn't feel real.

492
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:33,839
Am I

493
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,960
really getting married?

494
00:21:39,359 --> 00:21:41,079
Second Madam, Miss Lian.

495
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:45,039
Why are they here?

496
00:21:57,839 --> 00:21:58,920
Jinzhao.

497
00:22:02,480 --> 00:22:03,559
Jinzhao.

498
00:22:04,119 --> 00:22:05,559
Congratulations

499
00:22:05,839 --> 00:22:06,319
on securing

500
00:22:06,319 --> 00:22:07,880
such a wonderful match.

501
00:22:08,319 --> 00:22:09,759
Your uncle was overjoyed

502
00:22:09,759 --> 00:22:10,799
when he heard it.

503
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:11,559
He's drinking

504
00:22:11,559 --> 00:22:13,519
with your father right now.

505
00:22:20,480 --> 00:22:21,359
Jinzhao,

506
00:22:22,480 --> 00:22:24,519
what happened in the past

507
00:22:26,000 --> 00:22:29,119
was all because I was petty

508
00:22:29,279 --> 00:22:30,559
and short-sighted.

509
00:22:31,519 --> 00:22:33,000
My apology.

510
00:22:33,119 --> 00:22:34,119
Please don't.

511
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:44,720
Lian is so immature.

512
00:22:45,000 --> 00:22:46,039
I heard

513
00:22:46,039 --> 00:22:47,279
she quarreled with you today.

514
00:22:48,279 --> 00:22:49,279
Lian

515
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:51,200
has been spoiled by me.

516
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:52,759
She runs her mouth without thinking.

517
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:55,200
But deep down, she regrets it.

518
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:57,160
Isn't that right, Lian?

519
00:23:04,839 --> 00:23:05,880
I apologize.

520
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:08,319
I'm sorry.

521
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:12,200
You don't need to apologize to me.

522
00:23:12,720 --> 00:23:13,759
In this household,

523
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:15,359
you can't bully me.

524
00:23:17,079 --> 00:23:18,000
But

525
00:23:18,319 --> 00:23:20,079
you've bullied Lan over and over.

526
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:22,240
You should apologize to her.

527
00:23:22,519 --> 00:23:23,160
You...

528
00:23:23,799 --> 00:23:24,599
Yes, yes.

529
00:23:24,759 --> 00:23:26,279
Lian knows she was wrong.

530
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:27,119
We were
just about to

531
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:28,799
go to Lan's place.

532
00:23:29,559 --> 00:23:30,599
We're leaving.

533
00:23:31,799 --> 00:23:32,279
Let's go.

534
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:35,759
Miss,

535
00:23:36,359 --> 00:23:37,799
Second Madam sure changed

536
00:23:37,799 --> 00:23:38,920
her tune fast.

537
00:23:44,359 --> 00:23:45,480
I want to see Yanyun.

538
00:24:40,359 --> 00:24:41,680
[If you're ever in trouble,]

539
00:24:42,559 --> 00:24:44,200
[blow this whistle.]

540
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:12,200
[Will you]

541
00:25:12,519 --> 00:25:13,559
[marry me?]

542
00:25:21,519 --> 00:25:22,799
[If I ever face danger]

543
00:25:23,119 --> 00:25:24,839
[at court,]

544
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:26,279
[you can]

545
00:25:26,279 --> 00:25:27,440
[fill in the date]

546
00:25:27,759 --> 00:25:28,519
[on this divorce paper.]

547
00:25:29,440 --> 00:25:30,480
You can leave anytime

548
00:25:30,480 --> 00:25:31,599
without asking anyone.

549
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:33,559
Or use it

550
00:25:34,440 --> 00:25:35,559
when you

551
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:37,440
grow tired of me.

552
00:25:48,039 --> 00:25:48,799
It's raining.
Why not get out of the rain?

553
00:25:54,960 --> 00:25:56,480
You'll catch a cold, you know.

554
00:26:04,119 --> 00:26:04,880
Let me see.

555
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:12,759
Your hands are cold.

556
00:26:29,039 --> 00:26:29,799
What's wrong?

557
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:30,880
Why the rush to see me?

558
00:26:39,279 --> 00:26:39,920
I...

559
00:26:41,480 --> 00:26:42,720
I think I've lost my senses.

560
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:43,880
Lost your senses?

561
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:50,119
I was so happy

562
00:26:50,119 --> 00:26:51,200
when you sent Mrs. He

563
00:26:51,559 --> 00:26:53,000
to propose.

564
00:26:53,920 --> 00:26:55,319
But somehow,

565
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:56,480
I'm also

566
00:26:56,920 --> 00:26:58,039
worried.

567
00:26:58,559 --> 00:26:59,839
It doesn't feel real.

568
00:27:01,079 --> 00:27:02,000
I'm afraid

569
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:04,079
I'm being impulsive.

570
00:27:04,839 --> 00:27:05,640
What if

571
00:27:05,920 --> 00:27:07,680
I'm making a mistake?

572
00:27:08,640 --> 00:27:09,799
Making a mistake?

573
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,440
Let me finish.

574
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:16,000
I

575
00:27:16,319 --> 00:27:18,319
was feeling insecure.

576
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:20,680
But

577
00:27:21,720 --> 00:27:23,519
just now, when you walked over,

578
00:27:25,119 --> 00:27:26,160
somehow

579
00:27:26,599 --> 00:27:27,880
I suddenly felt

580
00:27:28,559 --> 00:27:29,519
that maybe

581
00:27:31,799 --> 00:27:33,039
I could

582
00:27:33,279 --> 00:27:34,200
take a gamble.

583
00:27:39,519 --> 00:27:40,680
You scared me.

584
00:27:41,319 --> 00:27:41,960
I thought...

585
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:43,279
You thought I'd back out?

586
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:47,880
Really?

587
00:27:48,319 --> 00:27:49,480
So you

588
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:50,680
get insecure too.

589
00:27:51,519 --> 00:27:52,200
Yeah.

590
00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:54,519
This is my weakness.

591
00:27:55,200 --> 00:27:56,440
So you have to keep my secret.

592
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:58,079
Can't let anyone know.

593
00:27:59,839 --> 00:28:00,599
Weakness?

594
00:28:00,920 --> 00:28:01,680
Me?

595
00:28:12,559 --> 00:28:13,079
Yes.

596
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:14,359
It's you.

597
00:28:31,839 --> 00:28:33,039
Chen Yanyun,

598
00:28:34,039 --> 00:28:35,119
I like you.

599
00:29:09,359 --> 00:29:11,319
This is my favorite hairpin.

600
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:12,759
Grandmother gave it to me.

601
00:29:14,960 --> 00:29:16,119
I'm giving it to you

602
00:29:16,839 --> 00:29:17,599
as an apology.

603
00:29:21,079 --> 00:29:22,400
Since Grandmother gave it to you,

604
00:29:23,319 --> 00:29:24,599
keep it for yourself.

605
00:29:26,839 --> 00:29:28,759
I've already humbled myself.

606
00:29:28,839 --> 00:29:30,039
What do you mean?

607
00:29:30,200 --> 00:29:31,440
Why are you putting on airs?

608
00:29:31,519 --> 00:29:32,000
You really are...

609
00:29:34,799 --> 00:29:35,440
Fine.
Whatever.

610
00:29:36,279 --> 00:29:37,200
I'll leave the hairpin here.

611
00:29:37,480 --> 00:29:38,480
Wear it if you want.

612
00:29:39,039 --> 00:29:39,920
Toss it

613
00:29:40,640 --> 00:29:41,599
if you don't.

614
00:29:42,559 --> 00:29:44,119
I've already apologized, anyway.

615
00:29:44,599 --> 00:29:46,039
Xiuju, let's go.

616
00:29:49,559 --> 00:29:50,319
Lian.

617
00:29:53,880 --> 00:29:54,519
What?

618
00:30:00,039 --> 00:30:00,960
I heard

619
00:30:01,319 --> 00:30:02,319
Yao Wenxiu

620
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:03,640
isn't a good person.

621
00:30:04,519 --> 00:30:05,599
I know you're engaged,

622
00:30:06,079 --> 00:30:07,640
but you should look into it.

623
00:30:08,279 --> 00:30:09,880
What do you mean by that?

624
00:30:10,319 --> 00:30:11,440
Wenxiu and I have known each other

625
00:30:11,440 --> 00:30:12,519
since we were kids.

626
00:30:12,680 --> 00:30:13,440
Don't I know

627
00:30:13,440 --> 00:30:14,480
what kind of person he is?

628
00:30:21,480 --> 00:30:22,599
I see.

629
00:30:23,599 --> 00:30:25,839
Jinzhao gets to marry Chen Yanyun,

630
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:28,680
and I'll marry Wenxiu.

631
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:30,599
You're the only one

632
00:30:30,599 --> 00:30:31,680
with nothing going on.

633
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:33,200
You're jealous,

634
00:30:33,359 --> 00:30:34,480
so you're trying to mess with me,

635
00:30:34,559 --> 00:30:35,079
right?

636
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:38,640
I've said what I had to say.

637
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:40,519
Believe it or not.

638
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:43,799
Instead of sticking your nose

639
00:30:43,799 --> 00:30:44,839
where it doesn't belong,

640
00:30:44,920 --> 00:30:46,359
worry about yourself.

641
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:47,759
Don't end up

642
00:30:47,759 --> 00:30:49,119
married to some penniless nobody.

643
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:51,079
How would Mr. Chen and Wenxiu

644
00:30:51,319 --> 00:30:52,599
be brothers in law with him then?

645
00:31:04,279 --> 00:31:06,039
Miss Lan is mean.

646
00:31:06,519 --> 00:31:07,440
She completely twisted

647
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:08,640
your good intentions.

648
00:31:11,279 --> 00:31:12,319
Let her be.

649
00:31:14,839 --> 00:31:16,039
I've done my part

650
00:31:17,839 --> 00:31:19,720
as her sister.

651
00:31:23,559 --> 00:31:24,240
That

652
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:25,759
ungrateful girl.

653
00:31:26,079 --> 00:31:27,359
Mr. Chen Yanyun came all this way

654
00:31:27,599 --> 00:31:29,839
and she didn't even write to tell me.

655
00:31:31,119 --> 00:31:32,079
Grandmother!

656
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:38,640
Jinzhao.

657
00:31:43,079 --> 00:31:44,519
Let me look at you.

658
00:31:50,119 --> 00:31:51,319
Grandmother.

659
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:57,799
My sweet girl.

660
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:01,640
They say Grand Secretary He's wife

661
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:02,960
is the matchmaker.

662
00:32:03,519 --> 00:32:04,319
And

663
00:32:04,799 --> 00:32:06,720
the Chief Councilor himself

664
00:32:06,880 --> 00:32:07,880
will preside over the wedding.

665
00:32:09,359 --> 00:32:10,440
I didn't expect him

666
00:32:10,759 --> 00:32:12,000
to go to such lengths.

667
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:15,839
Mr. Chen is giving you honor

668
00:32:16,559 --> 00:32:18,319
because you deserve it.

669
00:32:20,279 --> 00:32:21,839
You

670
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:24,359
are the finest girl in the world.

671
00:32:25,480 --> 00:32:26,720
Just let him do it.

672
00:32:29,319 --> 00:32:30,279
The other day,

673
00:32:30,519 --> 00:32:32,279
Mr. Chen suddenly came to propose.

674
00:32:32,799 --> 00:32:34,799
It caught me, your uncle, your aunt,

675
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:36,799
and Yao completely off guard.

676
00:32:37,599 --> 00:32:39,720
Your uncle and aunt aside,

677
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:41,119
Yao and I

678
00:32:41,359 --> 00:32:43,880
actually didn't approve.

679
00:32:45,440 --> 00:32:47,200
A great family is not an easy match.

680
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:49,240
Besides,

681
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:50,519
the Ji family

682
00:32:50,759 --> 00:32:53,200
carries the taint of being servants.

683
00:32:54,559 --> 00:32:57,440
The Chen family has

684
00:32:58,000 --> 00:32:59,519
a long noble heritage.

685
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:02,319
I was afraid

686
00:33:02,440 --> 00:33:04,039
you'd be mistreated.

687
00:33:06,599 --> 00:33:08,480
Even knowing you're not afraid,

688
00:33:08,839 --> 00:33:10,519
some hardships

689
00:33:10,720 --> 00:33:12,400
are better avoided.

690
00:33:12,920 --> 00:33:14,440
There's no need.

691
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:17,319
But who would've guessed

692
00:33:17,599 --> 00:33:19,680
he'd come with a divorce paper?

693
00:33:20,920 --> 00:33:22,279
Tell me, who brings

694
00:33:22,559 --> 00:33:24,119
a divorce paper

695
00:33:24,119 --> 00:33:25,440
when proposing?

696
00:33:26,240 --> 00:33:27,640
It left Yao and me

697
00:33:27,759 --> 00:33:29,720
lost for words.

698
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:46,160
Thought it through?

699
00:33:46,680 --> 00:33:47,880
You really want to marry Mr. Chen?

700
00:33:49,240 --> 00:33:50,799
I already said yes to him.

701
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:51,640
So what?

702
00:33:52,359 --> 00:33:53,319
If you're having second thoughts
and want to back out,

703
00:33:54,599 --> 00:33:55,240
I can help you

704
00:33:55,240 --> 00:33:56,359
call off the engagement.

705
00:33:58,200 --> 00:33:59,200
Aren't you afraid

706
00:33:59,440 --> 00:34:00,240
of offending Mr. Chen?
Why?

707
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:03,359
Worst case, I'll just quit the business.

708
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:05,599
He's our patron

709
00:34:05,759 --> 00:34:06,920
and a Grand Secretary.

710
00:34:07,440 --> 00:34:08,679
If you offend him,

711
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:10,440
you might lose more than just business.

712
00:34:10,960 --> 00:34:11,679
You could even

713
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:12,840
lose your life!

714
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:13,440
You...

715
00:34:14,920 --> 00:34:15,599
Gu Jinzhao!
What?

716
00:34:21,159 --> 00:34:22,760
This is a major decision for you.

717
00:34:23,519 --> 00:34:24,719
I'm just worried for you.

718
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:26,440
Fine.

719
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:27,559
Yao,

720
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:30,480
don't be upset.

721
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:32,239
I misspoke.

722
00:34:33,119 --> 00:34:34,159
I phrased it badly.

723
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:35,199
I'll stop.

724
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:38,920
Let me ask you again.

725
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:40,679
What are you thinking?

726
00:34:40,880 --> 00:34:41,760
Do you really want to marry him?

727
00:34:43,239 --> 00:34:43,880
Yes.

728
00:34:44,559 --> 00:34:45,639
You're sure?

729
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:48,559
Yes.

730
00:34:49,159 --> 00:34:50,440
You love him that much?

731
00:34:52,599 --> 00:34:53,119
Yes.
You really are...

732
00:34:54,239 --> 00:34:54,800
Grandmother.

733
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:57,760
Yao

734
00:34:58,000 --> 00:34:59,519
just can't bear to let you go.

735
00:35:02,320 --> 00:35:03,360
Girls mature and fly the nest.

736
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,519
You're the perfect example of that.

737
00:35:07,320 --> 00:35:08,679
Even after I marry,

738
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:10,239
I'll come back often to see you

739
00:35:10,480 --> 00:35:11,360
and Grandmother.

740
00:35:13,880 --> 00:35:15,280
I read that divorce paper.

741
00:35:15,760 --> 00:35:17,559
It looks like a backup plan for you.

742
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:19,440
But I know,

743
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:21,039
if something

744
00:35:21,159 --> 00:35:22,320
ever happens to Mr. Chen,

745
00:35:22,679 --> 00:35:23,639
given your nature,

746
00:35:23,920 --> 00:35:25,280
you'd never walk away.

747
00:35:26,079 --> 00:35:27,719
If I don't want to walk away,

748
00:35:28,079 --> 00:35:29,239
that just means

749
00:35:29,639 --> 00:35:30,800
I've found the right man.

750
00:35:34,559 --> 00:35:35,639
Grandmother.

751
00:35:36,719 --> 00:35:37,599
Yao.

752
00:35:38,760 --> 00:35:40,159
You two are my dearest family

753
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:41,360
in this world.

754
00:35:42,280 --> 00:35:43,440
I don't want to hide anything from you.

755
00:35:44,639 --> 00:35:45,199
Yes.

756
00:35:45,679 --> 00:35:47,039
I had already decided

757
00:35:47,320 --> 00:35:48,440
I wasn't going to marry.

758
00:35:49,440 --> 00:35:50,199
But then

759
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:52,440
Yanyun

760
00:35:52,599 --> 00:35:54,079
said he wanted to marry me,

761
00:35:55,199 --> 00:35:56,519
and slowly,

762
00:35:56,760 --> 00:35:57,599
I fell for him.

763
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:02,159
Like Yao said,

764
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:03,960
if something

765
00:36:04,519 --> 00:36:05,800
ever happens to Yanyun,

766
00:36:06,639 --> 00:36:07,920
I really can't be sure

767
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:09,000
I'd have the heart to leave.

768
00:36:10,119 --> 00:36:11,679
But for now, there's one thing

769
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:12,760
I am sure of.

770
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:14,719
Even if that day comes,

771
00:36:14,920 --> 00:36:16,079
I can still make a good life

772
00:36:16,079 --> 00:36:16,760
for myself.

773
00:36:20,239 --> 00:36:21,480
Right now,

774
00:36:23,760 --> 00:36:25,039
I'm willing to give it a try.

775
00:36:29,519 --> 00:36:31,159
Since you've said that,

776
00:36:31,800 --> 00:36:33,159
Yao and I

777
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:34,679
are reassured.

778
00:36:40,719 --> 00:36:41,880
This bracelet

779
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:44,559
was the gift your grandfather brought

780
00:36:44,840 --> 00:36:48,199
when he came to propose.

781
00:36:48,599 --> 00:36:50,480
It's been with me for decades.

782
00:36:51,159 --> 00:36:52,480
I'm giving it to you.

783
00:36:53,599 --> 00:36:54,800
Wear it,

784
00:36:56,440 --> 00:36:57,440
so it can

785
00:36:58,360 --> 00:36:59,920
remind you

786
00:37:00,360 --> 00:37:01,920
that if you run into trouble,

787
00:37:02,119 --> 00:37:03,480
you can always come back.

788
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:05,880
This is your home.

789
00:37:08,679 --> 00:37:09,320
Alright.

790
00:37:18,639 --> 00:37:19,360
Take care of yourself.

791
00:37:24,719 --> 00:37:25,880
Here's half your dowry.

792
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:28,639
So many banknotes.

793
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:54,719
Miss, you're back.

794
00:37:55,519 --> 00:37:57,039
Any letters for me these past few days?

795
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:57,960
No.

796
00:37:58,199 --> 00:37:59,920
Earlier, Old Madam's people came to say

797
00:38:00,039 --> 00:38:01,679
she wants to see you when you get back.

798
00:38:02,960 --> 00:38:03,639
Got it.

799
00:38:08,599 --> 00:38:09,960
Why hasn't Ye Xian come out of the palace?

800
00:38:10,960 --> 00:38:11,639
I'll go ask

801
00:38:11,639 --> 00:38:12,679
Guard Li again in a bit.

802
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:14,039
Okay.

803
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:27,719
Jinzhao, come here.

804
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:37,440
This

805
00:38:38,039 --> 00:38:38,880
is the dowry list

806
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:40,679
your mother left behind.

807
00:38:46,280 --> 00:38:47,199
Back then,

808
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:48,119
the Fourth Branch

809
00:38:48,119 --> 00:38:49,639
had just split off.

810
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:51,679
They rented a three-courtyard house.

811
00:38:51,920 --> 00:38:53,159
It was too small

812
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:55,320
to hold all these things.

813
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:58,239
So they were stored in my warehouse,

814
00:38:59,559 --> 00:39:01,320
under my care.

815
00:39:02,119 --> 00:39:03,679
Now that you're getting married,

816
00:39:04,320 --> 00:39:05,440
I should return

817
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:07,119
your mother's dowry

818
00:39:07,639 --> 00:39:08,559
to you in full.

819
00:39:12,800 --> 00:39:13,480
No!

820
00:39:30,039 --> 00:39:30,760
Alright.

821
00:39:31,239 --> 00:39:32,440
I'm a bit tired.

822
00:39:33,239 --> 00:39:34,559
You may all go back.

823
00:39:42,920 --> 00:39:43,639
Jinzhao.

824
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:49,199
Take good care of it.

825
00:39:52,440 --> 00:39:53,320
Thank you, Grandmother.

826
00:40:05,119 --> 00:40:05,719
What's wrong?

827
00:40:05,880 --> 00:40:06,800
Sad to see me
give all those assets

828
00:40:08,119 --> 00:40:08,960
to Jinzhao?

829
00:40:09,760 --> 00:40:10,599
I thought

830
00:40:10,599 --> 00:40:12,599
you'd give back half at most.

831
00:40:13,119 --> 00:40:13,840
I never expected you

832
00:40:13,840 --> 00:40:15,440
to give back everything.

833
00:40:15,440 --> 00:40:16,239
Those things

834
00:40:16,239 --> 00:40:17,880
belonged to Jinzhao's mother.

835
00:40:18,920 --> 00:40:20,239
If I held onto them,

836
00:40:20,760 --> 00:40:22,079
wouldn't they just come asking for them?

837
00:40:22,599 --> 00:40:23,920
I might as well

838
00:40:24,039 --> 00:40:24,679
just return them.

839
00:40:25,760 --> 00:40:27,840
This way, everyone saves face.

840
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:29,800
If she came

841
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:31,000
asking for them one day,

842
00:40:31,679 --> 00:40:32,519
I

843
00:40:33,079 --> 00:40:33,840
wouldn't even get

844
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:35,199
any credit for it.

845
00:40:36,039 --> 00:40:38,320
But what about Lian?

846
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:40,079
Many of those things

847
00:40:40,079 --> 00:40:41,599
were on Lian's dowry list.

848
00:40:41,679 --> 00:40:43,239
If the Yao family talks...

849
00:40:43,239 --> 00:40:44,519
If the Yao family talks,

850
00:40:44,679 --> 00:40:45,719
you talk back.

851
00:40:46,639 --> 00:40:47,519
Tell them

852
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:48,639
all those things

853
00:40:48,800 --> 00:40:49,760
went to Jinzhao.

854
00:40:50,719 --> 00:40:51,519
If they want them back,

855
00:40:51,719 --> 00:40:53,360
they can go ask Chen Yanyun.

856
00:40:54,960 --> 00:40:55,719
Honestly.

857
00:40:56,360 --> 00:40:57,639
What are you afraid of?

858
00:40:59,440 --> 00:41:00,800
Don't let Chen Yanyun's

859
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:02,360
idle days at home fool you.

860
00:41:02,639 --> 00:41:03,840
With his ability,

861
00:41:04,199 --> 00:41:06,119
he'll be back in office sooner or later.

862
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:07,440
Jinzhao

863
00:41:07,639 --> 00:41:09,159
will be a Grand Secretary's wife.

864
00:41:11,199 --> 00:41:13,360
You should teach Lian

865
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:15,719
some manners.

866
00:41:16,599 --> 00:41:17,639
Get her to associate more

867
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:19,800
with Jinzhao.

868
00:41:20,440 --> 00:41:21,519
Then let's see if the Yao family

869
00:41:21,679 --> 00:41:22,840
dares to bully her.

870
00:41:23,559 --> 00:41:25,880
Mother, you're right.

871
00:41:30,039 --> 00:41:31,079
Miss,

872
00:41:31,199 --> 00:41:32,840
you've seemed distracted lately.

873
00:41:33,440 --> 00:41:34,480
You noticed?

874
00:41:35,519 --> 00:41:36,800
I haven't slept in two nights.

875
00:41:39,199 --> 00:41:41,039
What will Xian do when he finds out

876
00:41:41,039 --> 00:41:42,320
Jinzhao is marrying

877
00:41:42,719 --> 00:41:43,599
Chen Yanyun?

878
00:41:43,760 --> 00:41:44,800
It worries me too.

879
00:41:45,199 --> 00:41:45,840
But Mr. Ye

880
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:47,079
will find out eventually.

881
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:48,000
Yeah.

882
00:41:48,440 --> 00:41:49,440
He'll find out sooner or later.

883
00:41:50,199 --> 00:41:51,519
But with his temper,

884
00:41:51,840 --> 00:41:52,480
who knows

885
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:53,599
what he might do.

886
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:54,679
Auntie!

887
00:41:56,079 --> 00:41:56,880
Jinzhao?

888
00:41:58,840 --> 00:41:59,559
Auntie,

889
00:41:59,840 --> 00:42:01,119
do you have a moment?

890
00:42:01,599 --> 00:42:02,559
I need to speak with you.

891
00:42:02,679 --> 00:42:03,280
I do.

892
00:42:03,519 --> 00:42:04,840
I'd like to talk with you too.

893
00:42:05,960 --> 00:42:06,480
Let's go.

894
00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:17,519
Sir,

895
00:42:18,239 --> 00:42:20,079
Miss Gu has been looking for you lately.

896
00:42:20,599 --> 00:42:21,880
She asked if you are free

897
00:42:21,880 --> 00:42:22,840
to meet with her tomorrow.
